Seven Kingdoms: Ancient Adversaries
-----------------------------------

Release version 2.14.3-test
Project website: www.7kfans.com

This is the release of the Seven Kingdoms: Ancient Adversaries source
code as authorized by Enlight by the 7kfans project.  The game is
provided under the terms of the GPL.  See the file "COPYING" for the
details of the license.

Changes in this release:
 * New network support using SDL_net, directly replacing DirectPlay.
 * Fixed saved games with marine units on x86_64.
 * Fixed the diplomacy menu in the Plague scenario.
 * Added multiplayer connection progress dialogs.
 * Added command line switches for future external lobby support.
 * Fixed fullscreen toggle on Windows.
 * Fixed the jumpy mouse.

Thanks to all who made this release possible.


Building the game
---------

General Requirements
* GCC 4.xx or later
* SDL 1.2
* SDL_net
* OpenAL
* Autoconf (using git snapshot)


Running
--------
You can download the game data if you do not already have the game
installed. You can find the game data from the 7kfans sourceforge
page at http://sourceforge.net/projects/skfans/

Copy the executable file "7kaa*" from the src/client directory to your
installed game directory.  Run the executable to start the game
instead of the classic Enlight version called 7k.exe.


